## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification (Browser)

1. Start the dev server:
   ```bash
   cd /home/okemwag/orcish-landing-page/apps/web && pnpm dev
   ```
2. Open `http://localhost:3000/signin` and log in
3. Navigate to `/dashboard`:
   - Confirm the 3-zone layout (top bar / map+intel / analytics strip)
   - Confirm the Kenya SVG map fills ~70% of the main area with colored regions
   - Click a region → confirm the intelligence panel on the right updates
   - Confirm the analytics strip at the bottom has 3 tabs that switch correctly
4. Navigate to `/dashboard/alerts` → confirm severity-bordered cards and timeline
5. Navigate to `/dashboard/drivers` → confirm rich bar chart and causal chain
6. Navigate to `/dashboard/interventions` → confirm card grid with ranked interventions
7. Navigate to `/dashboard/regional` → confirm map + enriched table
